snippet.title: Be Kind To Yourself — Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Be Kind To Yourself on Playdate Catalog: https://play.date/games/be-kind-to-yourself/

Next time I gotta check the display for dust particles :D (My setup was a bit wonky, so there’s not too many great combos, haha.)

Watch the Announcement Trailer here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hq6eoyDhhMg

Music by Seth Walker: https://soundcloud.com/sethamakessounds
https://freesound.org/people/Seth_Makes_Sounds/
